# Mbarara PM2.5 (CAMS NRT) — Weekly Time Series

This repo contains Google Earth Engine (GEE) scripts and analysis helpers to generate a weekly PM2.5 time series for Mbarara (Uganda) using ECMWF CAMS NRT.

## Data source
- GEE dataset: `ECMWF/CAMS/NRT`
- Variable: `particulate_matter_d_less_than_25_um_surface` (kg/m^3)
- Conversion: kg/m^3 × 1e9 = µg/m^3

## Workflow (recommended)
1. Run yearly (or smaller chunk) exports in GEE (scripts in `gee/`)
2. Download CSVs from Google Drive
3. Combine CSVs into one table (Power Query instructions in `scripts/`)
4. Plot in Excel; optionally compute monthly climatology (mean + range)

## Notes
- CAMS NRT is model-based and coarse resolution (~44 km). Treat as regional ambient background PM2.5.

## Repo contents
- `gee/` Earth Engine scripts for exports (including chunking around 2023-May failures)
- `scripts/` CSV combining + optional R/Python aggregation helpers
- `excel/` Excel-specific steps
